content: This app helped me break a 26 year habit! It's absolutely great!
This app is a must have for nail biters!!! I have been biting my nails to where they bleed for about 35 years or more. After listening to this app i have not biten my nails for 3 weeks now!!!

This program has worked for me so far in my journey to be free of a compulsion that I have suffered from since childhood. I have been using it regularly for 3 weeks, and I have not bitten my fingernails. You can choose to listen to the male or female therapist's voice. The Facebook page that goes with it is full of really supportive people as well. I recommend that you use both; do not try to go it alone. If I could make one improvement, I would like to see a few more different sessions (same therapists but different scripts) added, but all in all it is a wonderful app

Bitten my nails all my life. Listened to this as I was going to sleep. Didn't think it had really done anything at first but since installing it in August I've now got nails for the first time in 42 years. It really works and the fb group also really helps. The people on there encourage you and help greatly. Thank you so much Sue and James.
replyContent: Hi Kelly, thank so much for taking the time to write a review, we hugly apprecaite it. Also, a massive well done for your nail-biting (or not nail-biting!!) success! You are so right about the Facebook support group, wow what an incredible and supportive group it is! All the best Sue & James
